#: ../../B/beam.rst:5
msgid "beam"
msgstr "beam"

#: ../../B/beam.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../B/beam.rst:9
msgid "[from Star Trek Classic's \"Beam me up, Scotty!\"]"
msgstr "[Star Trek Classicの「Beam me up, Scotty!(転送してくれ、スコッティ!)」から]"

#: ../../B/beam.rst:12
msgid ""
"To transfer :ref:`softcopy` of a file electronically; most often in "
"combining forms such as beam me a copy or beam that over to his site."
msgstr ""
"ファイルの\\ :ref:`softcopy`\\ を電子的に転送すること。たいていはbeam me a copy(コピーを転送してくれ)やbeam "
"that over to his site(それを彼のサイトに転送しろ)のような複合形で使う。"

#: ../../B/beam.rst:15
msgid ""
"Palm Pilot users very commonly use this term for the act of exchanging bits "
"via the infrared links on their machines (this term seems to have originated"
" with the ill-fated Newton Message Pad). Compare :ref:`blast`\\, "
":ref:`snarf`\\, :ref:`BLT`\\."
msgstr ""
"Palm Pilotユーザーは、機器の赤外線リンクを介してビットを交換する行為を指してこの用語を非常によく使う(この用語は不運に終わったNewton "
"Message Padに由来するようだ)。\\ :ref:`blast`\\ 、\\ :ref:`snarf`\\ 、\\ :ref:`BLT`\\ "
"と比較せよ。"
